verbose_text: NGF signaling has also been linked to the expression of known sensory neuropeptides, CGRP and Substance P, in the rat gut [XREF_BIBR]; however, the direct source of NGF secretion is not known due to the diversity of cell types capable of its production [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: expression of known sensory neuropeptides, CGRP and Substance P
